Classes
Class
Description
Arrow
Represents an Arrow (i.e. to be drawn on a visual representation of a Board).
Board
This class represents a current position including all associated parameters (i.e. whose side it is to move, current en passant file, castling rights etc.)
ColoredField
Represents a Colored Square (i.e. to be drawn on a visual representation of a Board).
CONSTANTS
This class defines various static constants - mostly integers - used throughout the library.
Game
Class to store Games.
GameNode
Represents a node of a game tree.
HtmlPrinter
Render a html representation of the game.
JchesslibTest
Unit tests for jchesslib.
Move
Represents chess moves.
OptimizedRandomAccessFile
Wrapper of RandomAccessFile that has an readLine method performing similar to BufferedReader.readLine() while keeping the random access functionality.
PgnItem
Wraps information about a game within a PGN file.
PgnPrinter
render a PGN representation of the game
PgnReader
Read PGN files.
Polyglot
Reads opening books encoded to the Polyglot specification.
PolyglotEntry
Simple wrapper for polyglot book entries.
PolyglotExt
PolyglotExt is a simple bookformat of consecutive entries of 18 bytes each using a similar encoding as the original Polyglot.
PolyglotExtEntry
Simple wrapper for polyglot-ext book entries.
